dct_title_s: Geologic map of Anacapa and Santa Barbara Islands, Channel Islands National Park, Ventura and Santa Barbara Counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by contours and soundings.
"Prepared with the support and cooperation of the Santa Cruz Island Foundation, Santa Barbara, California."
Includes 2 col. cross-sections, location map, index map, note on sources of geology, ill., and conversion table.
Map of Anacapa Island includes inset of same area with shaded relief; map of Santa Barbara Island includes inset of same area with shaded relief, and 2 col. cross sections.
"Geologic map of Anacapa Island, map DF-73A"; "Geologic map of Santa Barbara Island, map DF-73B".
